'''Dipat''' is a Greek spiritual dance. It is the second-most popular [[Pontian Greeks|Pontian]] dance, behind only the [[Horon (dance)|Horon]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pontos-muenchen-ev.de/de/pontos/mousikoxoreutiki-paradosi/dipat/ |title=Χορός ΔιπάτDer Tanz DipatThe dance Dipat - Σύλλογος Ποντίων Μονάχου |website=Σύλλογος Ποντίων Μονάχου |language=de-DE |access-date=2017-09-14}}</ref>

