inopita]] * [[Taiyaki]] * [[Tarta de Santiago]] * [[Tea loaf]] * [[Teacake]] * [[Tin roof pie]] * [[Tipsy cake]] * [[Tiramisu]] * [[Torta alla Monferrina]] * [[Torta caprese]] * [[Torta de nata]] * [[Torta Maria Luisa]] * [[Torta Tre Monti]] * [[Torte]] * [[Tottenham cake]] * [[Tres leches cake]] * [[Tu (cake)|Tu]] * [[Tula pryanik]] * [[Tunis cake]] * [[Tunnock's teacake]] '''U''' * [[Upside-down cake]] '''W''' * [[Wacky cake]] * [[Wafer]] * [[Waffle]] * [[Wedding cake]] * [[Welsh cake]] * [[White sugar sponge cake]] * [[Wine cake]] '''Y''' * [[Yule log (cake)|Yule log]] '''Z''' * [[Zuger Kirschtorte]] * [[Zwetschgenkuchen]] {{div col end}}
