===Cookies=== {{main|List of cookies}} In the [[United States]] and [[Canada]] a [[cookie]] is a small, flat, baked treat, usually containing [[flour]], [[Egg (food)|eggs]], [[sugar]], and either [[butter]] or [[cooking oil]], and often including ingredients such as [[raisin]]s, [[oat]]s, or [[chocolate chip]]s.
