===Doughnuts=== {{main|List of doughnut varieties}} {{see also|List of fried dough foods}} A [[doughnut]], or donut, is a type of [[list of fried dough foods|fried dough]] [[confectionery]] or dessert food. The doughnut is popular in many countries and prepared in various forms as a sweet snack that can be homemade or purchased in bakeries, supermarkets, food stalls, and franchised specialty outlets.
