===Pastries=== {{main|List of pastries|List of poppy seed pastries and dishes}} {{see also|Pastry chef}} [[Pastry]] is the name given to various kinds of [[baking|baked products]] made from ingredients such as [[flour]], [[sugar]], [[milk]], [[butter]], [[shortening]], [[baking powder]], and [[Egg (food)|eggs]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/446138/pastry | title=Pastry | publisher=[[Encyclopædia Britannica]] | accessdate=3 January 2014}}</ref> Small [[tarts]] and other sweet baked products are called "pastries."
