===Pies=== {{main|List of pies, tarts and flans}} {{see also|Category:Tarts}} A [[pie]] is a baked dish which is usually made of a [[pastry]] dough casing that covers or completely contains a filling of various [[sweetness|sweet]] or [[Umami|savoury]] ingredients.
