==By region== ===Latin America=== [[Latin America]] is a highly diverse area with cuisines that vary from nation to nation. Desserts in [[Latin American cuisine]] include [[dulce de leche]], [[alfajor]], [[rice pudding]], [[tres leches cake]], [[Teja (confectionery)|teja]] and [[flan]].
===Southern Africa=== In [[Southern Africa]], desserts may simply be fruit, but there are some western style puddings, such as the [[Angola]]n [[cocada amarela]], which was inspired by [[Portuguese cuisine]].
